<item>
            <title>[HBASE-2492] &quot;BindException: Cannot assign requested address&quot; because all descriptors occupied in TIME_WAIT when random reading</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HBASE-2492</link>
                <project id="12310753" key="HBASE">HBase</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;See tail of hbase-2180 for detail on this issue.  If a lot of random reading, we start to us up descriptors because sockets stuck in TIME_WAIT.  Workaround described over in hbase-2180.  This issue covers fix for hdfs so we don&apos;t open a socket each pread.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
